347
00:32:31,866 --> 00:32:33,668
Never mind.

348
00:32:33,768 --> 00:32:34,936
How you guys doing?

349
00:32:35,036 --> 00:32:36,004
Good, buddy, you know.

350
00:32:36,104 --> 00:32:37,238
Just at the club.

351
00:32:37,338 --> 00:32:38,907
Yeah, sounds like it.

352
00:32:39,007 --> 00:32:42,577
Hey, how's Kerry?
