508
00:40:41,522 --> 00:40:42,423
Honey, thank you.

509
00:40:42,523 --> 00:40:43,424
Yup.

510
00:40:43,524 --> 00:40:44,825
And then-- oh, you know what?

511
00:40:44,925 --> 00:40:46,260
I could actually put a little bit in a bag,

512
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:47,428
